h1.font: Required permissions to create a subscription in project B for a topic in project A

div.p: The principal (user or service account) that is creating the subscription in project B must have the pubsub.topics.attachSubscription permission for the topic in project A. This permission is included in the roles/pubsub.subscriber role.

Here the subscription is created by the terraform service account of project B. Therefor we must give the roles/pubsub.subscriber role for the topic projects/project-a/topics/cloud-builds to terraform service account in project B.
